OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome late brightness around the Moray
OL,7,FFirth this evening. Meanwhile light
OL,8,Fand patchy rain moves into the west,
OL,9,Fbefore spreading northeast through the
OL,10,Frest of the night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,13,Fspots of light rain, but mainly dry
OL,14,Fwith some bright spells around the
OL,15,FMoray Firth. Showery outbreaks of rain
OL,16,Fwill then develop into the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
